message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and exceed your expectations. This product holds immense value to me, but I understand its true worth lies in finding the right person who can appreciate it fully. Given its significance to both of us, I propose a price of $9500 to ensure we both benefit from this transaction. I believe this is a fair compromise considering its market value and your appreciation for it. Let's make this collaboration beneficial for all parties involved.
